<li>My heart aches for your loss.</li>
<li>Sending love and strength during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and your family with heartfelt sympathy.</li>
<li>May your cherished memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li>With deepest condolences on the loss of your [relation].</li>
<li>Holding you and your family close in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
